@ThinkingandTinkering I just had an apiphony for you bro. for your wind capture device...

I was thinking, that you need to keep in mind the roof of the structure. You want some sort of re-direction off the roof to go back down.... The roof could have a funneled effect also. There would be gaps that any wind that blows up, would go up and into the middle tube going back down. That would all be built into the cap of the device and a central wind tube. Once you weave all the wind in the same direction, you can then use it more effectively.
Weaving The Wind 😀
